OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777119066
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion immediately
OL,4,Cdeducted points for financial breaches
OL,6,FWest Bromwich Albion have been handed
OL,7,Fan immediate two-point deduction for a
OL,8,Fbreach of financial rules, meaning
OL,9,Fthey are no longer safe from
OL,10,Frelegation.
OL,12,FThe club have been handed the
OL,13,Fdeduction because of a breach to the
OL,14,FEFL's Profit & Sustainability (P&S)
OL,15,Frules.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777119066
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion immediately
OL,4,Cdeducted points for financial breaches
OL,6,FIn response, the club have said that
OL,7,Fthis is "the smallest ever breach of
OL,8,Fthe P&S Rules across the EFL
OL,9,FChampionship and the Premier League"
OL,10,Fand that the club is "considering its
OL,11,Foptions" with regards to an appeal.
OL,13,FIt means the Baggies have dropped from
OL,14,F18th place with 52 points to 20th
OL,15,Fplace on 50 points, putting them six
OL,16,Fpoints above the drop zone with two
OL,17,Fgames to play.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777119066
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion immediately
OL,4,Cdeducted points for financial breaches
OL,6,FWest Brom, who previously thought they
OL,7,Fwere safe in the Championship, now
OL,8,Fneed just a point from their last two
OL,9,Fmatches to secure their Championship
OL,10,Fstatus.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the Baggies said:
OL,13,F"Following a two-day hearing which
OL,14,Fconcluded on 23 April 2026, the EFL's
OL,15,FClub Financial Review Panel (CFRP) has
OL,16,Fpublished a decision which states that
OL,17,Fthe Club has exceeded the Upper Loss
OL,18,FThreshold for the three-year period
OL,19,Fending 30 June 2025 and will therefore
OL,20,Freceive a two point deduction,
OL,21,Feffective immediately.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777119066
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion immediately
OL,4,Cdeducted points for financial breaches
OL,6,F"At this stage, the CFRP has not
OL,7,Fpublished any written reasons for the
OL,8,Fdecision. The Club disagrees with the
OL,9,FCFRP's findings and remains of the
OL,10,Fview that it has fully complied with
OL,11,Fthe Profitability and Sustainability
OL,12,F(P&S) Rules.
OL,14,F"The decision does not state the
OL,15,Famount by which the Club is said to
OL,16,Fhave exceeded the Upper Loss
OL,17,FThreshold. West Bromwich Albion has
OL,18,Fnot been informed of the quantum of
OL,19,Fthe breach, save that this is less
OL,20,Fthan #2million.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777119066
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion immediately
OL,4,Cdeducted points for financial breaches
OL,6,F"This is therefore the smallest ever
OL,7,Fbreach of the P&S Rules across the EFL
OL,8,FChampionship and the Premier League.
OL,10,F"Proceedings were brought by the EFL's
OL,11,FClub Financial Reporting Unit (CFRU)
OL,12,Ffollowing a change in the CFRU's
OL,13,Fapproach to Community Development
OL,14,FExpenditure.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777119066
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion immediately
OL,4,Cdeducted points for financial breaches
OL,6,F"In 2023/24, the CFRU accepted that
OL,7,Fthe Club was entitled to include in-
OL,8,Fkind donations of the Club's
OL,9,Ffacilities, staff time and resources
OL,10,Fto its official charity partner, The
OL,11,FAlbion Foundation, in its P&S
OL,12,Fcalculation.
OL,14,F"Earlier this year, the CFRU informed
OL,15,Fthe club that it had changed its
OL,16,Fapproach and imposed a retrospective
OL,17,Fadjustment to the Club's P&S
OL,18,Fcalculation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777119066
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion immediately
OL,4,Cdeducted points for financial breaches
OL,6,F"Without the CFRU changing its
OL,7,Fapproach to the Community Development
OL,8,FExpenditure, the Club would not have
OL,9,Fbreached the P&S Rules. The Club will
OL,10,Fcontinue to support the great work of
OL,11,FThe Albion Foundation and its
OL,12,Fcommunity programmes.
OL,14,F"West Bromwich Albion has a right of
OL,15,Fappeal and is considering its options.
OL,16,FThe Club will provide further comment
OL,17,Fonce it has received the written
OL,18,Freasons.
OL,20,F"For now, we will settle this on the
OL,21,Fpitch."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777119066
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion immediately
OL,4,Cdeducted points for financial breaches
OL,6,FIn a statement, the EFL said: "The
OL,7,Fsporting sanction has been applied to
OL,8,Fthe Championship table for the 2025/26
OL,9,Fseason.
OL,11,F"The Club may appeal the decision
OL,12,Fwithin 14 days of receipt of the full
OL,13,Fwritten reasons, as set out in
OL,14,FAppendix 6 of the Regulations. If an
OL,15,Fappeal is lodged, the rules provide
OL,16,Fthat it shall be heard within 28 days
OL,17,Fof submission.
OL,19,F"The full written reasons will be
OL,20,Fpublished in due course."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
